title: Meet the Office Klutz
description:
Meet the Office Klutz. Every office has one of these mishap-prone employees, but Staples has everything you need to manage his or her daily mayhem and messes, including lots and lots of paper towels. 

For more information, visit: http://bit.ly/1oAsqcX
